> The scanners bleeped as a bot approached. It was the one known as
>scorpinock. It came from DRillbit's group. He sent a comm on a frequency only
>he could pick up. It was impossible for anyone besides him to catch it. "Bot.
>You may enter the base."

"Whoa, uh yeah" Scorponok said as he approached the base, "I thought there
was no one in there. Cyber bee launch" his left claw opens up showing the
same cyber bee. It ejects and heads towards the base and Scoponok scuttles
over to some bushes to hide in. He activates a button and his eyes become
the eyes of the bee as he aproaches the base.
